Knock Madness is the upcoming third studio album by American rapper Hopsin. The album is scheduled to be released on November 26, 2013 by Funk Volume and distributed by Empire Distribution. Hopsin has said that the overall vibe of the album will be different from his previous album Raw and that he has said all he needs to about the Ruthless Records situation. The album contains guest appearances from rappers SwizZz, Dizzy Wright, Jarren Benton, and Tech N9ne among others. The album's production was primarily handled by Hopsin himself.
